OL,3,C10-month-old puppy shot with crossbow
OL,4,Cand abandoned
OL,6,FAn investigation has been launched
OL,7,Fafter a puppy was abandoned after
OL,8,Fbeing shot with a crossbow.
OL,10,FA member of the public found the 10-
OL,11,Fmonth-old female Belgian shepherd type
OL,12,Fbreed chained up at the side of the
OL,13,Froad in Boston, at the junction of the
OL,14,FA16 (Sibsey Road) and Pilleys Lane, on
OL,15,FTuesday (17 September).
OL,17,FShe was taken to a vet, who contacted
OL,18,Fthe RSPCA to investigate.
