OL,6,FAnimal Rescue Officer Dan Holman said:
OL,7,F"She is a very friendly dog and it is
OL,8,Fheartbreaking that she has gone
OL,9,Fthrough such a horrific experience. We
OL,10,Fjust don't know why someone would do
OL,11,Fthis to an innocent animal.
OL,13,F"The vets removed the bolt from her
OL,14,Fleg and she is making a good recovery.
OL,15,FDespite what she's been through, she
OL,16,Fis a friendly dog and loves being told
OL,17,Fshe is a good girl - she absolutely
OL,18,Fadores head and ear scratches too."
