OL,6,FThe dog is microchipped, with her name
OL,7,Fgiven on the chip as Nala. The RSPCA
OL,8,Fhas followed up the details on the
OL,9,Fchip but haven't been able to find the
OL,10,Fperson responsible.
OL,12,FDan Holman continued: "Because we
OL,13,Fdon't know where she came from, we're
OL,14,Fappealing to the public for help.
OL,16,F"If you have dashboard footage from
OL,17,Fthe area from that day we'd be
OL,18,Fgrateful if you got in touch. She was
OL,19,Ffound at around 7.30am, next to the
OL,20,Friver on the road, near to the golf
OL,21,Fcourse."
